<H1>MaraDNS tutorials and usage guides</H1>

MaraDNS includes a number of tutorials and usage guides which cover 
everything from teaching DNS basics for someone who has never administered
a DNS server before to usage guides on exotic things such as using
private CNAME records that point to public DNS entries.

<p>

For people who have never used DNS before, the <A href=dnsintro.html>DNS
introduction guide</A> is a good place to start.  For people who have
some experience with DNS servers, the <A href=quick_start.html>quick
start guide</A> is a good place to start.

